<h5 id="subject_224561">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d6c7ff8d7e6e6b36d5cd3fe3c34b7c33&amp;topic=28862.msg224561#msg224561" rel="nofollow">以前翻译的官方Abomination资料……</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_224561'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_224561'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #1 于:</strong> 2010-02-04, 周四 02:06:31 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_224561_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
